  "en_tr_ayubk": "Whatever verse We abrogate or cause to be forgotten, We bring one better than it, or the like of it; dost thou not know that God is powerful over everything?",
  "en_tr_sher": "Whatever message We abrogate or cause to be forgotten, We bring one better than that or the like thereof. Knowest thou not that God has the power to do all that He wills?",
